snippet.title: Blow the Hen down   Gameplay - Ludum dare 42
snippet.description:
Download it for free:  
https://nickzangus.itch.io/blow-the-hen-down

This is a game about pirates, hens, and devastating explosives!

Made in 72 hours for Ludum dare 42: "Running Out of Space".

---

All the contents were created during the 72h except for the followings:

Song “Silver Spear” by Slainte
Sound Effects by Soniss
Chicken model by Kednar
Font “Black Pearl” by JoannaVu
